Frequently Asked Questions about High-voltage Traction Inverter Market
What is a high-voltage traction inverter?
A high-voltage traction inverter is a critical component in electric and hybrid vehicles that converts the direct current (DC) from the battery into the alternating current (AC) that is used to operate the vehicle's electric motor.

